            "last_activity_date": 1520264715,
            "creation_date": 1520264493,
            "body": "<p>You can use <code>replaceAll<\/code> with a regexp.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>tempPhrase = sentence.replaceAll(\"[.,!?:;]\" , \" \");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
